OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1784224105
OL,3,CHundreds of passengers disrupted in
OL,4,CGatwick airport chaos
OL,6,FA number of flights were diverted from
OL,7,FGatwick airport after an emergency was
OL,8,Fdeclared when a plane temporarily
OL,9,Fblocked its only runway in use on
OL,10,FWednesday.
OL,12,FHundreds of passengers were affected
OL,13,Fas planes preparing to land were
OL,14,Fforced to divert or enter holding
OL,15,Fpatterns.
OL,17,FIt was a British Airway flight from
OL,18,FPalma de Mallorca that blocked the
OL,19,Frunway.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/4
