OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1784224105
OL,3,CHundreds of passengers disrupted in
OL,4,CGatwick airport chaos
OL,6,FIt reported an issue with its nose
OL,7,Fwheel.
OL,9,FThe plane landed safely but remained
OL,10,Fon the runway ` during its removal the
OL,11,Frunway closed for 29 minutes.
OL,13,FBritish Airways said, "Our flight
OL,14,Flanded safely and customers
OL,15,Fdisembarked normally following reports
OL,16,Fof a technical fault with the aircraft"
OL,18,FEmergency services met the plane as a
OL,19,Fprecaution upon landing.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/4
