OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1784224105
OL,3,CHundreds of passengers disrupted in
OL,4,CGatwick airport chaos
OL,6,FAffected flights came from holiday
OL,7,Fhotspots such as Tenerife, Lanzarote,
OL,8,FGreece and Morocco.
OL,10,FPassengers were diverted to airports
OL,11,Faround the UK including Luton,
OL,12,FStansted and Heathrow. Other flights
OL,13,Fhad to delay landing, circling in the
OL,14,Fair while waiting for the runway to
OL,15,Freopen.
OL,17,FGatwick Airport is now back in
OL,18,Foperation.
OL,20,FA London Gatwick spokesperson said:
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/4
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
