OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1784224105
OL,3,CHundreds of passengers disrupted in
OL,4,CGatwick airport chaos
OL,6,F"Earlier this morning, the runway was
OL,7,Fclosed for a short period due to a
OL,8,Ftechnical issue with an aircraft.
OL,10,F"As a result, a small number of
OL,11,Fflights were diverted, with the
OL,12,Fmajority later returning to London
OL,13,FGatwick.
OL,15,F"As always, safety and security is our
OL,16,Fnumber one priority."
